text: God Help the Girl is a 2014 British musical drama movie written and directed by Stuart Murdoch. At the Sundance Film Festival it won the World Cinema Dramatic Special Jury Award (Ensemble). ==Cast== *Emily Browning - Eve *Olly Alexander *Hannah Murray *Pierre Boulanger Category:2014 musical movies Category:2014 drama movies Category:British musical movies Category:British drama movies Category:Movies directed by Stuart Murdoch
